First Department,

December, 1943.

(December 3, 1943.) G. Schirmer, Inc., Respondent, v. Robbins Music Corporation et al., Appellants.

Order unanimously affirmed, with twenty dollars costs and disbursements, with leave to the defendants to answer within ten days after service of order on payment of said costs. No opinion. Present •— Townley, Glennon, Untermyer, Dore and Cohn, JJ. [176 Misc. 578.]
